com.customlbs.library.model

Class TileKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.customlbs.library.model.TileKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public final class TileKey
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable

    Class to identify single tiles.

    A tile is exactly identified to which Building, Floor, TileKey (zoom level) at which position (x,y) it belongs.

    See Also:
    TileRequester, Indoors.getTileRequester(com.customlbs.library.TileRequester.TileRequestCallback)
